{
  "texts": [
    "3.4.1 Question 7: what criteria are participants using to distinguish text generated by an AI from that written by a human?",
    "Two coders were recruited to separately analyze the criteria given by the participants for making their choice in considering a text to have been written by a human or an AI.",
    "They were asked to create categories of factors that participants used to justify their choices and to place the justifications in these categories.",
    "Inter-coder reliability was very high, with a Cohen's kappa of κ = 0.935, p < 0.001, indicating almost perfect agreement between both coders.",
    "After discussion between the two coders in order to revise the categorizations, perfect agreement was attained for all cases (κ = 1.0)."
  ]
}